name: Enlightenment (EFL) MIT-Style License
notes:
Per Fedora, this license is a modified version of the common MIT license,
with an additional advertising clause that makes it GPL-incompatible. It
was originally found at
http://www.enlightenment.org/viewvc/e16/e/COPYING?revision=1.10 , but that
URL is gone (they seem to have moved source control systems). The latest
available copy from enlightment.org
http://trac.enlightenment.org/e/browser/trunk/E16/e/COPYING has been
preserved here for reference.
